<br>
Aldrin, you've had your say in other threads, and I am KINDLY asking you to hold your comments from this thread.<br>
<br>
Everyone else -- PLEASE do not try to inflame anyone.  I'm trying to have a mature conversation.<br>
<br>
----<br>
<br>
There's been some concerned that the guilds are trying to hurt the unguilded.  I happen to feel this is inaccurate.<br>
<br>
An unguilded individual has exactly as much opportunity to attend the planes as a guilded individual.<br>
<br>
You are just as welcome to assemble a force for the FiF days.  You can even try to take a single group in on a FFA day.<br>
<br>
There will be one public event on the schedule at a time -- which is just as many events as an individual guild will have.<br>
<br>
